Definition: spectroscope for obtaining a mass spectrum by deflecting ions into a thin slit and measuring the ion current with an electrometer
Synonyms: spectrometer, adj, pert, spectrometric, spectroscope, for, obtaining, a, mass, spectrum, by, deflecting, ions, into, thin, slit, and, measuring, the, ion, current, with, an, electrometer
Category: noun.artifact
